00"> • </span><a href="https://lithub.com/the-literary-film-tv-you-need-to-stream-in-april"><span style="font-weight: 400">Literary film and TV you need to stream in April</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> • </span><a href="https://bookmarks.reviews/the-best-reviewed-books-of-the-month-3-29-2024/"><span style="font-weight: 400">March’s best reviewed books</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> • </span><a href="https://lithub.com/more-stories-more-voices-on-the-importance-of-the-smallish-book-publisher/"><span style="font-weight: 400">Kristen McGuiness considers the essential role independent publishing houses play</span></a><span style="font-weight: 400"> </span></p>
										
																				
